dsword and a dark humor darker than her portals.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xQ7p30CVNi7VLBYbYSq8A.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 78, 0);\"><strong>Golem (Bruno):</strong></span> Gentle clay giant who’d crush a car to save a kitten but still can’t figure out doorknobs.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/JNyDkxX4CPrfwoI8EO0SF.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(157, 133, 133);\"><strong>Coupé (Janelle):</strong></span> Ex-assassin with metallic wings and a heart colder than her umbrakinetic knives.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/sByvKjGLc6Xczi_wm3nPW.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 242, 255);\"><strong>Prism</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 53, 140);\"><strong>(Alice)</strong></span><strong>:</strong> Photokinetic diva who judges your life choices through a holographic visor.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/r1OAUULXS7_kJgPsf0eeK.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 143, 254);\"><strong>Robert Robertson III:</strong></span> Burned-out ex-hero dispatcher hiding Mecha-Man’s scars under SDN khakis.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/up--Rfh_mcxrEfebSv4-R.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 2);\"><strong>Phenomaman (Katon-Ur)</strong></span><strong>:</strong> Alien himbo superhero who thinks grandstanding counts as therapy.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/iCsBh7KEIrbK7-Z2tLnEC.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(10, 173, 223);\"><strong>Waterboy (Herm):</stron